{
  "stem": "5970.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we had teachers coming to the house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took us in small groups.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we carried on with schoolwork for as long as we could at the beginning of the occupation, while the Germans were still sorting themselves out and sort of settling in.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that was that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But straight from the beginning, there were different-- there-- there were-- there was a tremendous change in our lifestyle.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "First of all, we had to wear the armbands with the-- with the Star of David on them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there were millions of restrictions and decrees coming out every single day-- a curfew in the evenings.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We're not allowed to get out-- to come out of the house, although we were still lucky to be in our own home.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Part of it was requisitions by a German officer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he lived in part of our apartment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The rest we had to share.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So it wasn't as comfortable as before.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But still, we somehow managed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And everybody had to work straight from the beginning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So my father had a shoe factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they needed him for the war effort.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So he carried on manufacturing shoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But obviously, it was for the Germans now, not for-- for customers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he didn't get paid either.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "The-- the-- all the leather that he had and all this stuff was just requisitions.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he had to supply the stuff that they wanted.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we-- we were busy studying whatever we could.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But outside, it became very ugly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "There were roundups.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Especially they collected all the religious Jews that were wearing these black coats and-- and yarmulkes and-- and looked to them strange.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They were beating them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They were arresting them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They were torturing people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We heard of people being arrested for no reason whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
